Object Test Case of Water Bottle

Check the size of the water Bottle.
Check the body shape of the Water Bottle.
Check the branding of the water Bottle Company.
Check the label of the water bottle is it directly printed on the bottle's body or external label?
Check the weight of the empty water bottle.
Check the color of the water bottle.
Check the Cork shape of the Water Bottle.
Check the Cork style of the Water Bottle.
Check whether the cork fits the bottle body.
Check if there is an option to hold the Cork like strip, handle etc.
Check if there is an option to carry the water bottle.
Check if there is any lock option at Water Bottle Cork.
Check the material of the water bottle like plastics, steel etc.
Check if the Water bottle has any straw.
Check the middle body of the water bottle is there any style to grip the bottle nicely?
Check the the water bottle is it foldable or not? 
Check the bottom of the water bottle is it flat? 
Check the capacity of the water Bottle. 
Check whether the water bottle is multi-purpose or single-use.
Check the number of inside layers of the water bottle.
Check the layers of materials in the water bottle.
Check the water bottle if there is an option to show the inside temperature of the water.

